Optimization


Code
ff &lt;- function(x){
  y &lt;- -3*x^4+4*x^3
  return(y)
}
x &lt;- seq(-1, 2, length.out = 1000) 
y &lt;- ff(x)
tibble(x, y) |&gt; 
  ggplot(aes(x, y)) +
  geom_line() + theme_bw()

Numerical Optimization


Code
ff &lt;- function(x){
  y &lt;- -3*x^4+4*x^3
  return(-y)
}

optimize(ff, c(-5,5))


#&gt; $minimum
#&gt; [1] 1
#&gt; 
